w">Thu vãn thuỵ giác - 秋晚睡覺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C3%8Dch-T%E1%BA%AFc/author-2WHplYhGibS3kNKVcV5ntg">Trần Ích Tắc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-H%E1%BB%A9a-b%C3%A1t-th%E1%BA%ADp-di-quy-Giang-Ninh-c%E1%BA%ADn-t%E1%BB%89nh-Ph%E1%BB%A7-t%C3%ADch-th%C3%AC-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-kh%C3%A1ch-du-th%E1%BB%AD-huy%E1%BB%87n-%C6%B0-H%E1%BB%A9a-sinh-x%E1%BB%AD/poem-AW0---HTvRURdc6cklmfTw">Tống Hứa bát thập di quy Giang Ninh cận tỉnh, Phủ tích thì thường khách du thử huyện ư Hứa sinh xử khất Ngoã Quan tự Duy Ma đồ dạng chí chư thiên mạt - 送許八拾遺歸江寧覲省甫昔時嘗客遊此縣於許生處乞瓦棺寺維摩圖樣志諸篇末</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Chi-C%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-xu%E1%BA%A5t-s%E1%BB%A9-An-Nam/poem-Dr_E1GOkiKuCANoXqyQcQg">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh xuất sứ An Nam - 送尚書柴莊卿出使安南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Chi-C%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-hAavXOrXmwKq4z80V_fZhg">Vương Chi Cương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BB%B3-b%C3%A0-h%C3%A0nh/poem-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Tỳ bà hành - 琵琶行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/V%C4%83n-d%E1%BA%A1-ch%C3%A2m/poem-qn1yGMgdnwtiE0K9YF-20w">Văn dạ châm - 聞夜砧</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br></div>	</div>
